The paper deals with the problem of architecture search in deep learning, which is a topic that falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG). The specific application domain is image classification (cs.CV), but the paper also discusses results in the domains of disparity estimation (a dense regression task) and language modelling, which could fall under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
